org.opendaylight.controller.networkconfig.neutron.northbound

Class NeutronLoadBalancerListenerNorthbound

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.networkconfig.neutron.northbound.NeutronLoadBalancerListenerNorthbound

  • public class NeutronLoadBalancerListenerNorthbound
extends java.lang.Object
    Neutron Northbound REST APIs for LoadBalancerListener Policies.
    This class provides REST APIs for managing neutron LoadBalancerListener Policies

    Authentication scheme : HTTP Basic
    Authentication realm : opendaylight
    Transport : HTTP and HTTPS

    HTTPS Authentication is disabled by default. Administrator can enable it in tomcat-server.xml after adding a proper keystore / SSL certificate from a trusted authority.
    More info : http://tomcat.apache.org/tomcat-7.0-doc/ssl-howto.html#Configuration
